author: dlydick
msg: Added '-lm' to linkage step for various floating point function calls.
Corrected use of 'echo "text" $echoc"' constructions to use '$echon'
instead.  This should make script work for _all_ shades of /bin/sh.
Added explicit CONFIG_CPUTYPE variable that hold CPU architecture type.
Added explicit CONFIG_OSNAME variable that hold operating system name.
